---
description: Nuxt 4 + Nuxt UI 4 edge template conventions
globs: '**/*.{vue,ts,css}'
alwaysApply: true
---

- Nuxt 4 structure: all frontend code in `app/`, Nitro server in `server/`
- Cloudflare Workers: NO Node.js modules (`fs`, `path`, `crypto`). Use Web Crypto API.
- Nuxt UI 4: `USeparator` not `UDivider`. Icons use `i-` prefix. Use token colors.
- Tailwind CSS 4: configure via `@theme` in `app/assets/css/main.css`
- SEO: every page must call `useSeo()` + a `useSchemaOrg()` helper
- Data fetching: use `useAsyncData`/`useFetch`, never raw `$fetch` in `<script setup>`
- SSR state: use `useState()` or Pinia, never bare `ref()` at module scope
- Architecture: thin components, thick composables. No inline business logic in templates.
- See `AGENTS.md` at project root for full details and audit workflows.
